OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FSacked teacher vows to     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fdefend 20 years of absence 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A teacher in Italy who was sacked for  
OL,6, 20 years of absence in 24 years at     
OL,7, schools near Venice has vowed to tell  
OL,8, her side of the story.                 
OL,10,FCinzia Paolina De Lio was dismissed in 
OL,11,F2017 after she reappeared for four     
OL,12,Fmonths and triggered complaints.       
OL,14,FItaly's highest court confirmed the    
OL,15,Fdismissal after a legal battle, saying 
OL,16,Fher absences showed a "permanent and   
OL,17,Fabsolute ineptitude".                  
OL,19,FMs De Lio has condemned the ruling and 
OL,20,Fvowed to "reconstruct the truth".      
